title: Turkmen State Institute of Architecture and Construction
text: The Turkmen State Institute of Architecture and Construction (formerly named as Turkmen Polytechnic Institute) is one of the major universities in <a href="Turkmenistan">Turkmenistan</a>. It is generally the leading institute in the country in engineering and energy. A number of noted Turkmen politicians studied at the university, particularly those in the economic sector including <a href="Annaguly%20Deryayev">Annaguly Deryayev</a>, <a href="Khodjamyrat%20Geldimyradov">Khodjamyrat Geldimyradov</a>, <a href="Yagshigeldy%20Kakayev">Yagshigeldy Kakayev</a>, <a href="Khadyr%20Saparlyev">Khadyr Saparlyev</a>, <a href="Hydyr%20Saparly%C3%BDew">Hydyr Saparlyýew</a> and <a href="T%C3%A4%C3%A7berdi%20Tagy%C3%BDew">Täçberdi Tagyýew</a>.
